#!/usr/bin/env python
"""
SConstruct for the standalone GDScript linter (homot-linter).

This is a BUILD MANIFEST documenting what's needed. The linter cannot be
built fully standalone because it depends on core/ types (Variant, String,
HashMap, etc.) which are tightly coupled to the engine.

PRACTICAL BUILD APPROACH:
    The linter is built as a second Program target within the engine's
    SCons build. Add the following to the root SConstruct after line
    `SConscript("platform/" + env["platform"] + "/SCsub")`:

        if env.get("linter", False):
            SConscript("linter/SCsub")

    Build commands:
        # Alongside an editor build (reuses editor libs, ~145MB):
        scons platform=windows target=editor linter=yes

        # Minimal size (~61MB, needs template_debug libs):
        scons platform=windows target=template_debug linter=yes

        # Development (with debug symbols, ~220MB):
        scons platform=windows target=editor dev_build=yes linter=yes

    This produces bin/homot-linter alongside the main engine binary.

    The template_debug target is recommended for distribution: it strips
    TOOLS_ENABLED code from engine libs (biggest size win) while keeping
    DEBUG_ENABLED for GDScript warnings.

FILES COMPILED (linter-specific):
    linter/main_linter.cpp              - CLI entry point + engine bootstrap
    linter/linter_run.cpp               - Lint logic (collect, pre-scan, analyze)
    linter/stubs/linterdb.cpp           - JSON data store
    linter/stubs/classdb_stub.cpp       - ClassDB stub + StubMethodBind
    linter/stubs/engine_stub.cpp        - Engine::has_singleton() stub
    linter/stubs/project_settings_stub.cpp - ProjectSettings stub
    linter/stubs/resource_loader_stub.cpp  - ResourceLoader stub
    linter/stubs/script_server_stub.cpp    - ScriptServer stub

LINKED AGAINST (subset):
    core           - Variant, String, Object, FileAccess, etc.
    drivers        - FileAccess/DirAccess platform implementations
    servers        - TextServerDummy (GDScript tokenizer dependency)
    module_gdscript - GDScriptParser, GDScriptAnalyzer, GDScriptCache
    module_holymolly - HOMOT language extensions

    Scene, editor, and unrelated modules are NOT linked.
    Stubs override ClassDB/Engine/ProjectSettings/ResourceLoader/ScriptServer
    at link time (stub .obj listed before engine .lib).
"""
